text: Aleksandr Korobov (born 1 April 1978) is a Kazakhstani ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 2002 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Kazakhstani male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Kazakhstan Category:Ski jumpers at the 2002 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Almaty
